03:18:24,500 --> 03:18:29,500
We are very small in this Universe.

12792
03:18:29,500 --> 03:18:32,500
There's so much to be discovered out there.

12793
03:18:32,500 --> 03:18:37,500
And from what we feel, from what Dr. Italu perceived,

12794
03:18:37,500 --> 03:18:41,500
extraterrestrials are at peace, they live in peace.

12795
03:18:41,500 --> 03:18:46,500
They're curious, but they live in peace, and can contribute a lot to us.

12796
03:18:46,500 --> 03:18:52,500
So, since man has reached the Moon, why not advance a little further?

12797
03:18:52,500 --> 03:18:55,500
And of course, it's no longer just the Varginha ET.

12798
03:18:55,500 --> 03:19:01,500
He is a Brazilian ET, an American ET, a Chinese ET, a Russian ET.

12799
03:19:01,500 --> 03:19:03,500
He belongs to all of us, to the planet.

12800
03:19:03,500 --> 03:19:07,500
And why not investigate this better, for ufology to advance further, right?

12801
03:19:07,500 --> 03:19:11,500
Even recently, didn't you speak to friends who had seen the craft?

12802
03:19:11,500 --> 03:19:14,500
There are people who have seen things like that.

12803
03:19:14,500 --> 03:19:19,500
When James Fox returns to Varginha, I'll introduce him to another three or four people,

12804
03:19:19,500 --> 03:19:24,500
